SIMPLE: nonuser
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nonuser
<hw>Non*us"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <sn>1.</sn> <def>A not using; failure
to use.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>An office may be forfeited by misuser or <qex>nonuser</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Blackstone.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>Neglect or omission to use an
easement or franchise or to assert a right.</def>
<rj><au>Kent.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nonvascular</ent>⟦br⟧
